=== create_a_report_in_snow ===

--- Items ---
> SNow access
> Report Perms

--- Procedure ---
1. Open up ServiceNow
2. In the left hand menu, type in the search box: "Reports" then go to "View/Run"
3. In the top right, select "Create a report"
4. Maintain Source type: "Table", Table: "Security Incidents...", choose "Next".
5. Do not choose a visualisation
6. In the right hand window, you will see a blank report. You will also see a filter button, select this button.
7. Choose your filters: Opened > on > Last month and customer is <business name>
8. From there you have everything need, save

Congratulations, you have successfully created a snow report.
